      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Option is one of the most lucrative and money making financial instrument available today. If correct <a title="Option Trading" href="http://www.optiontradebasics.com/Getting-Started-With-Options">Option Trading</a> System and Strategy is employed then a trader can make a fortune out of trading in this instrument. Options are a type of derivatives or extension on a particular underlying asset. Below are some of the underlying assets for which options are available today:</p>
<p>1.)    Index Options</p>
<p>2.)    Stock Options</p>
<p>3.)    Commodity Options</p>
<p>4.)    Currency Options</p>
<p>5.)    Precious Metal Options</p>
<p>Option is basically a contract between a buyer and a seller where buyer of the contract has a right to buy or sell the underlying asset at a predefined strike price before the contract end date. Buyer of the contract has a right but he/she is not obligated to exercise their rights. There are two types of options, Call and Put. Call option gives the buyer of the contract a right to buy an underlying asset, while Put option gives buyer of the contract a right to sell an underlying asset. If a trader is bullish about the market he can choose to buy Call options and if a trader is bearish about the market he can choose to buy Put options.</p>
<p>If options have great profit potential then it also have a power to drag a trader into heavy losses if he/she doesn’t know basics of <a title="Options trading" href="http://www.optiontradebasics.com/Getting-Started-With-Options">Options trading</a>. So it’s important to get familiar with <a title="fundamentals of options trading" href="http://www.optiontradebasics.com/options-trading-basics/fundamentals-of-options-trading/">fundamentals of options trading</a> and then start investing your own money. Once you are fundamentally clear about options trading next step is to make strategies. There are several strategies like Straddle and Option spread where a trader buys and sells option where he/she can earn profits depending upon how far the market price goes from the strike price immaterial of the direction. So with these strategies in place may the market be bull or bear it works in favor of the trader.</p>
<p>Keeping this in mind trader should learn the fundamentals and create a spread strategy which gives unlimited profits with limited risk out of Option Trading System.</p>
