Similar Option Trade news:&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.optiontradebasics.com/options-trading-basics/learn-trade-options-successfully/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Learn To Trade Options Successfully'&gt;Learn To Trade Options Successfully&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;Options trading have opened up a new horizon for the...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.optiontradebasics.com/options-trading-system/realtime-benefit-market-options-trading-software/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Take Real-time Benefit of the Market with Options Trading Software'&gt;Take Real-time Benefit of the Market with Options Trading Software&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;Good knowledge is the key for trading options with handsome...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href='http://www.optiontradebasics.com/options-trading-basics/options-trading-basics-frequently-asked-questions/' rel='bookmark' title='Permanent Link: Options Trading Basics – Frequently Asked Questions'&gt;Options Trading Basics – Frequently Asked Questions&lt;/a&gt; &lt;small&gt;Before a trader tries to design any strategy for trading...&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/option-trade-basics/Option_Trade_Basics-Trading_Options_Online_At_Your_Comfort_And_Convenience.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Any trader would firstly need to look at all the available financial instruments before deciding the one which best suits his/her current portfolio. He/she can look at the advantages, disadvantages, risks, revenue and expenses of all the instruments. If a trader has decided to trade in options, then he/she needs to decide the medium of trading that is offline <a title="options trading" href="http://www.optiontradebasics.com/Getting-Started-With-Options">options trading</a> (through  the phone) or online options trading(over the internet). Some of the conventional traders go with offline trading where they have the investment money sitting into their trading account; so whenever they wish to trade they can pick up a phone and call the brokerage firm who manages their brokerage account.</p>
<p>Some of the non conventional and new generation of traders find the option of online trading much more appealing considering the advantages it has to offer. For online trading one needs to know basics of computers and internet. Online trading may follow any of the two formats mentioned below:</p>
<p>1.)    Web based format: In the web based format you only need to have internet access and a web browser loaded on your computer which is pretty common these days, so as long as you have this available you can start trading from any part of the world. One can manage online options trading in the same way they log in and manage their bank account.</p>
<p>2.)    Software based format: In the software based format one needs to install software on the computer, so they can do trading only on that computer or any other computer which has the required software.</p>
<p>Developers of these formats take utmost care that the trading is as simple as possible for the traders which eliminate the time required to learn web based or software based trading formats. Apart from providing a trading platform these applications also provide excellent management tools which make the expense and revenue tracking of the portfolio pretty smooth for the traders. These online applications also send real time trading tips to the traders to take advantage of changing market movements.</p>
<p>One of the best advantages of online trading is: if there is a market opportunity then the trader can make a decision and do real time trading, where as if a trader is trading offline he may need to wait on the phone for his/her turn and by the time the price he is looking for might have changed.</p>
